Type    = Summon Dandan (4/1)
Cost    = UU
Artist  = Drew Tucker

Text(5E): Islandhome (If defending player controls no islands, this
          creature cannot attack. If you control no islands, bury
          this creature.)

Text(CR): Cannot attack if defending player controls no islands. If at any
          time you control no islands, bury Dandan.

